title_bed_bats_review: Rental unit in Dhaka · 1 bedroom · 1 bed · 2 baths
listing_description:
Hello, I’m Efa and I live in a wonderful location of Dhaka centered among many popular attractions and night life. Here, you will have your own private room with balcony and half bathroom with western toilet.

The common area shared with my mother and I, includes a bathroom with shower, kitchen, and dining area which you are welcome to use as your own.

Please note that at this time we are only able to welcome women travelers, as well as men who are traveling with a female family member.
